<% p  = {5 =>"I strongly do not relate", 4 => "I rarely ralate", 3 => "I sometimes relate", 2 => "I usually relate", 1 => "I always relate"}%>
<body class="bg-ques">
  <div class="mx-0 container mt-20 px-10 mx-sm-auto">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header" style="background-color:#223C60;">
        <h2 class="card-title text-center text-white mt-2">New Survey</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        <div class="text-center">
          <i class="far fa-file-alt fa-4x mb-3 text-primary"></i>
          <h4>
            <strong class="title-color">Your Survey From : <%= @survey.created_at %></strong>
          </h4>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you feel feverish, have flu-like chills, or a fever with an oral temperature of 38Â°C or higher?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
         <%= p[ @survey.fever_chills ] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you have a cough or has a chronic cough gotten worse recently?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.cough] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Are you experiencing trouble breathing or shortness of breath?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.difficulty_breathing] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you feel an unusually intense fatigue for no obvious reason? how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.fatigue] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you have unusual headache for no specific reason?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.headache] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Have you had a sudden loss of smell and loss of taste?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.sensory_loss] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you have a sore throat?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.sore_throat] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">do you suffer from nausea of an unknown cause?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.nausea] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you suffer from unusual unstability in your digestive system eg.diarrhea?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.diarrhea] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <p><strong class="px-3 title-color">Do you have unusual or unexplained muscle pain, or stiffness (not related to physical activity)?, how much can you rete your case?</strong></p>
        <div class="form-check title-color mb-2">
          <%= p[@survey.body_ache] %>
        </div>
        <hr />
        <div class="form-outline mb-4">
          <h5 class="text-center "><strong class="mb-0 title-color">Your comment:</strong></h5>
          <div class="title-color text-center" >
            <%= @survey.comment%>
          </div>
            
        </div>
        <div class="card-footer text-center">
          <%= link_to 'Back', profile_path(@profile), :class => "btn btn-sign  mb-3" %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>